column7: Q2. How much are ABC values being reflected in your day-to-day decisions? Motivation - ABC possess internal enthusiasm to develop their minds and improve their skills, even when faced with obstacles. They give their best effort, follow through on obligations, and strive for goals. Integrity - ABC demonstrate an honest and truthful character. They seek to be trustworthy and genuine with others. Engagement - ABC participate enthusiastically in all aspects of the program and immerse themselves in the college experience. Community - ABC display a mindset that honors and upholds those around them. They build connections with fellow participants, support one another, and encourage each other to achieve their goals. Curiosity - ABC demonstrate a sincere desire to learn. They explore opportunities to grow with an open-mind and excitement.
